@startuml SD_07_SepayPayment
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - SePay VietQR Payment
' FR-20: QR Payment + Webhook Auto-confirm + Ticket Issuance
' ============================================================

title **SD-07: SePay VietQR Payment\n(Generate QR → Bank Transfer → Webhook → Confirm → Issue Tickets)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #E8F5E9
    ParticipantBorderColor #2E7D32
    ArrowColor #2E7D32
}

actor "Attendee" as Customer #LightBlue
participant "Browser\n(JSP + JS)" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "PaymentServlet\n(Controller)" as Controller #E8F5E9
participant "PaymentFactory" as Factory #FFF3E0
participant "SepayPaymentService" as SepaySvc #E8F5E9
participant "OrderService" as OrderSvc #E8F5E9
participant "TicketService" as TicketSvc #E8F5E9
participant "OrderDAO" as OrdDAO #FFF3E0
participant "TicketDAO" as TktDAO #FFF3E0
box "External" #F5F5F5
    participant "SePay\nAPI" as SePay #FFCDD2
    participant "Bank\n(VietQR)" as Bank #BBDEFB
end box
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

== Part A: Display Payment QR ==

Customer -> Browser: Proceed to payment
Browser -> Controller: GET /checkout/payment\n?orderId={id}
activate Controller

Controller -> OrderSvc: getOrder(orderId)
activate OrderSvc
OrderSvc -> OrdDAO: findById(orderId)
activate OrdDAO
OrdDAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM Orders\nWHERE orderId = ?\nAND customerId = ?
activate DB
DB --> OrdDAO: Order
deactivate DB
OrdDAO --> OrderSvc: order
deactivate OrdDAO
OrderSvc --> Controller: order
deactivate OrderSvc

Controller -> Factory: getProvider("sepay")
Controller -> SepaySvc: createPayment(order)
activate SepaySvc
SepaySvc -> SepaySvc: Build transfer info:\nbankCode, accountNumber,\namount = order.totalAmount,\ncontent = "ST" + order.orderCode\n(identifier for webhook matching)
SepaySvc -> SepaySvc: Generate VietQR URL:\nhttps://qr.sepay.vn/img?\nacc={account}\n&bank={bank}\n&amount={amount}\n&des={content}
SepaySvc --> Controller: PaymentResult {\n  qrUrl, bankName,\n  accountNumber, amount,\n  content (transfer note),\n  expiresIn: 15min\n}
deactivate SepaySvc

Controller --> Browser: Forward → payment.jsp\n(QR code, bank info,\n15-minute countdown)
deactivate Controller
Browser --> Customer: Payment page:\n- QR Code (large)\n- Bank: MB Bank\n- Account: 0389118xxx\n- Amount: 1,500,000 VND\n- Note: ST-ORD-A1B2C3\n- ⏳ 15:00 countdown

== Part B: Customer Pays ==

Customer -> Browser: Open banking app\nand scan QR
Browser -> Bank: Scan QR → Auto-fill\ntransfer details
Customer -> Bank: Confirm transfer
activate Bank
Bank -> Bank: Process payment
Bank --> Customer: ✅ Transfer successful
Bank -> SePay: Transaction notification
deactivate Bank

== Part C: Webhook Auto-confirm ==

SePay -> Controller: POST /api/payment/sepay-webhook\n{\n  "gateway": "MBBank",\n  "transactionDate": "2025-01-15",\n  "accountNumber": "0389118xxx",\n  "transferType": "in",\n  "transferAmount": 1500000,\n  "content": "ST ORD-A1B2C3",\n  "referenceCode": "FT25015xxx",\n  "description": "ST ORD-A1B2C3"\n}\nHeaders: Authorization: Bearer {API_KEY}
activate Controller

Controller -> Controller: **5-Layer Webhook Validation:**\n1. ✅ API Key matches\n2. ✅ transferType == "in"\n3. ✅ Content-Length ≤ 1MB\n4. ✅ Parse orderCode from content\n5. ✅ Amount matches order

Controller -> OrderSvc: confirmPayment(\n"ORD-A1B2C3", amount, refCode)
activate OrderSvc

OrderSvc -> OrdDAO: findByOrderCode("ORD-A1B2C3")
activate OrdDAO
OrdDAO -> DB: SELECT * FROM Orders\nWHERE orderCode = 'ORD-A1B2C3'\nAND status = 'pending'
activate DB
DB --> OrdDAO: Order
deactivate DB
OrdDAO --> OrderSvc: order
deactivate OrdDAO

OrderSvc -> OrdDAO: updatePayment(orderId)
activate OrdDAO
OrdDAO -> DB: UPDATE Orders SET\nstatus = 'confirmed',\npaymentDate = GETDATE(),\ntransactionId = ?\nWHERE orderId = ?
activate DB
DB --> OrdDAO: Updated
deactivate DB
OrdDAO --> OrderSvc: OK
deactivate OrdDAO

' --- Issue Tickets ---
OrderSvc -> TicketSvc: generateTickets(order)
activate TicketSvc

loop for each OrderItem (qty times)
    TicketSvc -> TicketSvc: ticketCode = "TKT-" +\ncrypto random 8 chars
    TicketSvc -> TicketSvc: qrCodeData = JWT.sign({\n  ticketId, ticketCode,\n  eventId, orderId\n}, SECRET)
    TicketSvc -> TktDAO: create(Ticket)
    activate TktDAO
    TktDAO -> DB: INSERT INTO Tickets (\n  ticketId, orderId, orderItemId,\n  ticketCode, qrCodeData,\n  isCheckedIn=0, createdAt\n)
    activate DB
    DB --> TktDAO: Created
    deactivate DB
    TktDAO --> TicketSvc: OK
    deactivate TktDAO
end

TicketSvc --> OrderSvc: tickets (generated)
deactivate TicketSvc

' --- Send Notification ---
OrderSvc -> DB: INSERT INTO Notifications\n(userId, type='ORDER_CONFIRMED',\nmessage='Payment confirmed!\n5 tickets issued for\nevent {title}')

OrderSvc --> Controller: PaymentConfirmed
deactivate OrderSvc

Controller --> SePay: HTTP 200 OK\n{"success": true}
deactivate Controller

== Part D: Customer Gets Confirmation ==

Browser -> Controller: GET /api/payment/check-status\n?orderId={id}\n(JS polling every 3s)
activate Controller
Controller -> OrdDAO: findById(orderId)
activate OrdDAO
OrdDAO -> DB: SELECT status FROM Orders
activate DB
DB --> OrdDAO: status = 'confirmed'
deactivate DB
OrdDAO --> Controller: confirmed
deactivate OrdDAO
Controller --> Browser: JSON {status: "confirmed"}
deactivate Controller

Browser -> Browser: ✅ Payment confirmed!\nAuto-redirect to tickets page

Browser --> Customer: 🎉 Payment successful!\n5 e-tickets issued.\nView your tickets.

@enduml
